source.name: Northern Southern Hunting Zone Line
source.description: This data depicts the east-west line that separates northern and southern hunting zones in New York State. Although every effort has been made to ensure the accuracy of information, errors may be reflected in the data supplied. The user must be aware of data conditions and bear responsibility for the appropriate use of the information with respect to possible errors, original map scale, collection methodology, currency of data, and other conditions.
